    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_4",
      "block_index": 4,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "character_list",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "杨延嗣：净",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 5,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_5",
      "block_index": 5,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "情节",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 2,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_6",
      "block_index": 6,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "宋辽失和，使杨继业征之。杨继业兵困两狼山，遣子七郎求救于元帅潘洪。潘洪不发一兵，且杀七郎以报私仇。杨继业久困无援，夜梦七郎冤魂，醒后大疑。使子六郎突围出，己则单身杀至苏武庙，气力不加，见李",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 94,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_7",
      "block_index": 7,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "陵碑，大骂一场，竟撞碑死。",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 13,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_8",
      "block_index": 8,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "根据《戏考》第二册整理",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 11,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_9",
      "block_index": 9,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "【第一场】",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 5,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_10",
      "block_index": 10,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（杨延嗣上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_11",
      "block_index": 11,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延嗣",
      "text": "赤胆忠心，只落得，青史名标。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 14,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延嗣",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "引子"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_12",
      "block_index": 12,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延嗣",
      "text": "我乃七郎阴魂是也。只因那日回朝颁兵，可恨潘洪将我射死芭蕉树上。不免前去与我父托兆。众鬼卒，宋营去者！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 41,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延嗣",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_14",
      "block_index": 14,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延嗣",
      "text": "我杨家保宋主忠心秉正，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延嗣",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄导板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_15",
      "block_index": 15,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延嗣",
      "text": "东西征南北剿哪得安宁。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延嗣",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄原板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_16",
      "block_index": 16,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延嗣",
      "text": "金沙滩打一仗父子被困，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延嗣",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_17",
      "block_index": 17,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延嗣",
      "text": "老爹爹他命我回朝颁兵。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延嗣",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_18",
      "block_index": 18,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延嗣",
      "text": "潘洪贼想起了打子仇恨，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延嗣",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_19",
      "block_index": 19,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延嗣",
      "text": "他将我绑芭蕉乱箭穿身。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延嗣",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_20",
      "block_index": 20,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延嗣",
      "text": "叫鬼卒驾阴风宋营来进，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延嗣",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_21",
      "block_index": 21,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延嗣",
      "text": "见了那老爹爹细说分明。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延嗣",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_22",
      "block_index": 22,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（杨延嗣下。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_23",
      "block_index": 23,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "【第二场】",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 5,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_24",
      "block_index": 24,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（杨继业上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_25",
      "block_index": 25,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "金乌坠玉免升黄昏时候，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄导板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_26",
      "block_index": 26,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "盼姣儿不由人珠泪双流，我的儿吓！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 16,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "回龙"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_27",
      "block_index": 27,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "命七郎回大营颁兵求救，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄原板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_28",
      "block_index": 28,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "为什么此一去不见回头？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_29",
      "block_index": 29,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "莫不是潘仁美又下毒手，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_30",
      "block_index": 30,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "怕的是我的儿性命难留。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_31",
      "block_index": 31,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "含悲泪进宝帐双眉愁皱，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_32",
      "block_index": 32,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "西北风吹的我遍体飕飕。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_33",
      "block_index": 33,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（杨延昭上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_34",
      "block_index": 34,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延昭",
      "text": "听谯楼打罢了二更时分，杨延昭倒做了巡营之人。迈步儿且把那宝帐来进，又只见老爹爹瞌睡沉沉。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延昭",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_38",
      "block_index": 38,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（杨延嗣上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_39",
      "block_index": 39,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延嗣",
      "text": "听谯楼打罢了三更时分，半空中来了我七郎阴魂。叫鬼卒驾阴风宝帐来进，又只见老爹爹瞌睡沉沉。我这里将他的忠魂惊醒，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延嗣",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄原板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_44",
      "block_index": 44,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "猛抬头又只见七郎姣生。我命你回大营颁兵求救，为什么哭啼啼头带雕翎？恨不得下位去将儿抱定，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄原板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_48",
      "block_index": 48,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延嗣",
      "text": "老爹爹休贪睡细听分明：金沙滩打一仗父子被困，老爹爹命孩儿回朝颁兵。潘洪贼想起了打子仇恨，他将我绑芭蕉乱箭穿身。回头来又对六兄论，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延嗣",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄原板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_54",
      "block_index": 54,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "小弟言来听分明：高堂老母要你孝敬，莫学小弟不孝顺。我本当与六兄多谈多论，又恐怕天明亮难回天庭。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 8,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_59",
      "block_index": 59,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（杨延嗣下。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_60",
      "block_index": 60,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "适才间梦见了七郎来临，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄导板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_61",
      "block_index": 61,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "呀！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 2,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_62",
      "block_index": 62,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "又只见六郎儿瞌睡沉沉。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄原板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_63",
      "block_index": 63,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "六郎儿醒来！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 6,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_64",
      "block_index": 64,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延昭",
      "text": "适才间梦见了七弟来临，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延昭",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄导板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_65",
      "block_index": 65,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延昭",
      "text": "又只见老爹爹面前存。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 10,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延昭",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_66",
      "block_index": 66,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延昭",
      "text": "爹爹，适才睡梦之中，观见七弟浑身是血，头带雕翎。不知是何缘故？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 31,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延昭",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_67",
      "block_index": 67,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "为父亦得此兆。这才是“梦梦相同，必有凶险”。我亦有意，命你回朝探听七弟下落。不知我儿意下如何？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 47,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_68",
      "block_index": 68,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延昭",
      "text": "爹爹年迈，孩儿放心不下。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延昭",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_69",
      "block_index": 69,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "为父虽然年迈，倒也康健，只管前去。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 17,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_70",
      "block_index": 70,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延昭",
      "text": "孩儿不去！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延昭",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_71",
      "block_index": 71,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "儿吓，为父倒有父子之情，难道你无手足之义么？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 22,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_72",
      "block_index": 72,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延昭",
      "text": "爹爹不必如此，孩儿去就是了。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 14,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延昭",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_73",
      "block_index": 73,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延昭",
      "text": "辞别爹爹跨金蹬，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 8,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延昭",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_74",
      "block_index": 74,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延昭",
      "text": "不分昼夜去颁兵。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 8,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延昭",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_75",
      "block_index": 75,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延昭",
      "text": "爹爹，我父，啊呀！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 9,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延昭",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "哭"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_76",
      "block_index": 76,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（杨延昭下。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_77",
      "block_index": 77,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "六郎上了马能行，好不叫人痛伤心。悲悲切切大营进，父子相会再等来生。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 8,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_81",
      "block_index": 81,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（杨继业下。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_82",
      "block_index": 82,
      "scene_id": "s_3",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "【第三场】",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 5,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_83",
      "block_index": 83,
      "scene_id": "s_3",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（耶律休上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_84",
      "block_index": 84,
      "scene_id": "s_3",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_耶律休",
      "text": "俺奉太后之命，巡营了哨。就此前往。呔！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 19,
      "speaker_name_raw": "耶律休",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_85",
      "block_index": 85,
      "scene_id": "s_3",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（杨延昭上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_86",
      "block_index": 86,
      "scene_id": "s_3",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延昭",
      "text": "何人挡住某家去路？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 9,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延昭",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_87",
      "block_index": 87,
      "scene_id": "s_3",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_耶律休",
      "text": "俺乃耶律休，要你的狗命！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "speaker_name_raw": "耶律休",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_88",
      "block_index": 88,
      "scene_id": "s_3",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延昭",
      "text": "一派胡言！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延昭",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_89",
      "block_index": 89,
      "scene_id": "s_3",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（杨延昭、耶律休同开打，耶律休败下，杨延昭下。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "打",
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 24,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_90",
      "block_index": 90,
      "scene_id": "s_4",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "【第四场】",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 5,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_91",
      "block_index": 91,
      "scene_id": "s_4",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（杨延昭上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_92",
      "block_index": 92,
      "scene_id": "s_4",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨延昭",
      "text": "且住，且喜逃出虎口，不免回朝便了！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 17,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨延昭",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_93",
      "block_index": 93,
      "scene_id": "s_4",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（杨延昭下。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_94",
      "block_index": 94,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "【第五场】",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 5,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_95",
      "block_index": 95,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（杨继业、四老军同上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_96",
      "block_index": 96,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "叹杨家秉忠心大宋扶保，到如今只落得瓦解冰消。恨胡儿打来了连环战表，他要夺我主爷锦绣龙朝。贼潘洪在金殿挂了招讨，我父子倒做了马前英豪。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "反二黄慢板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_102",
      "block_index": 102,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "金沙滩双龙会一战败了，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "反二黄原板"
      ],
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_103",
      "block_index": 103,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "只杀得血成河鬼哭神号。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_104",
      "block_index": 104,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "我的大郎儿吓，替宋王把忠尽了，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 15,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_105",
      "block_index": 105,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "二郎儿短剑下命赴阴曹。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_106",
      "block_index": 106,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "杨三郎被马踏尸骨难找，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_107",
      "block_index": 107,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "四、八郎在番邦无有下梢。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_108",
      "block_index": 108,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "五郎儿在五台修真学道，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_109",
      "block_index": 109,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "七郎儿被潘洪箭射芭蕉。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_110",
      "block_index": 110,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "只剩下六郎儿东征西剿，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_111",
      "block_index": 111,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "可怜他又尽忠，又尽孝，身披盔甲、马不停蹄，东荡西剿，昼夜杀砍，为国勤劳。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 36,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_112",
      "block_index": 112,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "可怜我八个子把四子丧了，我把四子丧了，我的儿吓！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 24,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_113",
      "block_index": 113,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "一家人只落得死无下梢。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_114",
      "block_index": 114,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "恨萧营报前仇又打战表，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_115",
      "block_index": 115,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "请我主赴两狼摆一摆枪刀。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_116",
      "block_index": 116,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "这潘洪二次里挂了招讨，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_117",
      "block_index": 117,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "我父子做先行逢山开路，遇水安桥。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 16,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_118",
      "block_index": 118,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "黄道日不发兵不把贼剿，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_119",
      "block_index": 119,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "黑道日命父子去把兵交。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_120",
      "block_index": 120,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "为国家哪顾得黄道黑道，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_121",
      "block_index": 121,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "我父子一马当先杀进了贼巢。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 13,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_122",
      "block_index": 122,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "头一阵得了胜回营禀报，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_123",
      "block_index": 123,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "狗奸贼将人马扎定了城濠。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_124",
      "block_index": 124,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "传一令将胡儿斩杀尽了，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_125",
      "block_index": 125,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "斩不尽杀不绝不许回朝。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_126",
      "block_index": 126,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "二次里闯贼巢入了圈套，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_127",
      "block_index": 127,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "我父子困焦牙入了笼牢。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_128",
      "block_index": 128,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "我也曾命六郎回营去了，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_129",
      "block_index": 129,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "可怜我为国家，秉忠心，年迈苍苍，困两狼，里无粮，外无草，盼兵不到、盼子不归，我这老残生，就不能还朝！我的儿吓！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 55,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_130",
      "block_index": 130,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_四老军",
      "text": "饿吓！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 3,
      "speaker_name_raw": "四老军",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "同白"
      ],
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_131",
      "block_index": 131,
      "scene_id": "s_5",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_杨继业",
      "text": "饥饿了你就该战马斩倒，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "杨继业",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "反二黄原板"
      ],
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
